p82
aVMost of them won't move at all,
p83
aVbut some of them might make a tiny step.
p84
aVThose are then selected by the algorithm,
p85
aVreproduced with mutation and recombinations to introduce sex as well.
p86
aVAnd you repeat that process over and over again,
p87
aVuntil you have something that walks \u2014
p88
aVin this case, in a straight line, like this.
